Package com.microsoft.azure.management.resources.fluentcore.arm.collection

Interface SupportsBatchDeletion

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    ActionGroups, ApplicationGateways, BatchAccounts, BatchAIClusters, BatchAIFileServers, CdnProfiles, ContainerGroups, DiagnosticSettings, Disks, DnsZones, EventHubNamespaces, Identities, LoadBalancers, ManagementLocks, NetworkInterfaces, Networks, NetworkSecurityGroups, NetworkWatchers, PublicIPAddresses, RedisCaches, RouteTables, ServiceBusNamespaces, Snapshots, SqlServers, StorageAccounts, TrafficManagerProfiles, VirtualMachineCustomImages, VirtualMachines, VirtualMachineScaleSets

    public interface SupportsBatchDeletion
    Provides access to deleting multiple resource from Azure, identifying them by their IDs.

    (Note this interface is not intended to be implemented by user code.)
